item.title: Kellie add a quote by Jeffrey Brown
item.description:
"-Here's a pretty shell for you.
-Oh, thank you my baby.
-Look, here's another one!
-Thank you.
-Look at this pretty one!
-Thank you.
-Here's a REALLY pretty one.
-Um, thank you.
" -- Jeffrey Brown

item.title: Kellie add a quote by J.K. Rowling
item.description: "Of course it is happening inside your head, Harry, but why on earth should that mean that it is not real?" -- J.K. Rowling

item.title: Kellie add a quote by Jodi Picoult
item.description: "When we're awake, we see what we need to see. When we're asleep, we see what is really there." -- Jodi Picoult

item.title: Kellie add a quote by Alice Walker
item.description: "I think it pisses God off if you walk by the color purple in a field somewhere and don't notice it. People think pleasing God is all God cares about. But any fool living in the world can see it always trying to please us back." -- Alice Walker

item.title: Kellie add a quote by Liz Prince
item.description: "Whoa dude. My belt came undone when you said that." -- Liz Prince
